name: The Unknown - Manic Chord
description:
Welcome alien trackers to this SFS extra-terrestrial finder. This app will help you find alien friends all over the Deer Shed festival site! Just walk around and you'll be sure to meet some.
You can work your way up through the ranks by meeting more aliens! If you get to level 6 make sure you show someone at the SFS council.
Watch out for random objects which can be kept in your gift store and offered to aliens in return for extra points.
Well what are you waiting for? Off you go and see what you can discover!
